description: Attackers abuse this service to expose malicious servers on a *.trycloudflare.com subdomain

The subdomain .trycloudflare.com is a temporary hostname provided by Cloudflare Tunnel - It allows users to expose local services to the internet without needing to configure port forwarding or a public IP - attackers frequently abuse it for malicious activities
